These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, lemonade
1. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
House: modern, palace
1. the palace house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| House   | modern | palace |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
There 2 different types of food: watermelon, corn
